# Docs maintenance

After each feature slice:
- update relevant `product-os/02-features/*.md`
- update `product-os/06-status/daily-log.md`
- update `product-os/06-status/done-log.md`
- update `product-os/06-status/current-focus.md`
- update ADR if architectural decision changed
- if spec behavior changed, update `TRACEBUD_V1_2_EUDR_SPEC.md` and cross-reference impacted sections in status logs
